href="https://lifehacker.com/home/throw-a-packing-party-to-declutter-your-home" target="_blank">打包派对</a>”技巧等方法时，您可以使用框进行分类和排序。</p><p> 12-12-12 方法要求您每天扔掉 12 件物品，捐赠 12 件，并保留 12 件。显然，你不会每天带12件物品到捐赠中心，但你可以把它们放在一边，稍后一次性全部拿走。另一方面，彼得·沃尔什方法要求你清理整个房间，弄清楚你真正<em>想要</em>从房间里得到什么，然后只放回符合该愿景的物品。其余的——你猜对了——被扔掉或捐赠。虽然您可以使用纸板箱来存放这些东西，但最好买一些更坚固的东西，特别是如果您计划一个房间一个房间地重复您的过程并在过程中重复使用盒子。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-4 shadow-lg"><div class="order-1 mx-auto md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:flex md:w-full md:grow md:flex-col"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left"> HOMZ 重型 31 夸脱模块化塑料可堆叠玩具收纳箱</div><div class="mt-2 hidden md:flex md:grow md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"> <span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">44.99 美元</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-full rounded-md bg-brand-green py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm text-white"><span>了解更多</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HW8STF8DCYDNFS2TAQWEWKEC/images-1.fill.size_245x222.v1713987468.jpg" alt="HOMZ 重型 31 夸脱模块化塑料可堆叠玩具收纳箱" width="245" height="222" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-2 mt-2 hidden w-64 md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:block"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HW8STF8DCYDNFS2TAQWEWKEC/images-1.fill.size_245x222.v1713987468.jpg" alt="HOMZ 重型 31 夸脱模块化塑料可堆叠玩具收纳箱" width="245" height="222" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-5 w-full"><div class=" hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-ful